---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Callout from '../../components/Callout.astro';

export const title = "Westbrook Dispensary Guide";
---

<Layout 
  title="Westbrook Dispensary Guide | Maine Dispensary Guide" 
  description="Complete guide to opening a cannabis dispensary in Westbrook, Maine. Market analysis, regulations, and investment requirements."
  heroImage="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500916434205-0c77489c6cf7?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1200&h=400"
>
  <article>
    <div class="article-header">
      <h1>Westbrook Dispensary Guide</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">How to open a cannabis dispensary in Westbrook, Maine</p>
    </div>

    <section>
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>Westbrook, Maine's tenth-largest city with 32,000+ residents, is located just 7 miles west of Portland in the Greater Portland Metro area. Known for its growing tech sector, historic mills, and family-friendly community, Westbrook offers an exciting opportunity for cannabis entrepreneurs seeking access to the Portland market without Portland's premium costs. Before moving forward, familiarize yourself with the <a href="/guides/maine-cannabis-real-estate/">real estate requirements</a> essential for success.</p>
    </section>

    <Callout title="Westbrook: A Local Opportunity" type="passion">
      Operating in Westbrook is more than just a business; it's about becoming a pillar of the community. Focus on local engagement and education to build lasting trust with your neighbors.
    </Callout>


    <section>
      <h2>Why Westbrook?</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Portland Proximity</strong> - Just 7 miles from Portland's massive market</li>
        <li><strong>Growing Population</strong> - 32,000+ residents with steady growth</li>
        <li><strong>Lower Costs</strong> - More affordable than Portland proper</li>
        <li><strong>Tech Hub</strong> - Young professional demographic</li>
        <li><strong>Easy Access</strong> - Located on I-95, excellent visibility</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Westbrook Market</h2>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Factor</th><th>Assessment</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Population</td><td>32,000+</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Metro Area</td><td>Portland Metro (500k+)</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Competition</td><td>Low-Moderate</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Real Estate</td><td>Moderate ($18-25/sq ft)</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Access</td><td>I-95, Route 25</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Local Regulations</h2>
      <p>Westbrook has adopted local cannabis regulations. Under <a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/rules" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Maine OCP rules</a>, you'll need to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Obtain state license from Maine Office of Cannabis Policy</li>
        <li>Apply for local approval from Westbrook</li>
        <li>Meet zoning requirements for commercial districts</li>
        <li>Comply with distance requirements from schools</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Best Locations</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Main Street</strong> - Historic downtown corridor</li>
        <li><strong>Route 25</strong> - High traffic retail area</li>
        <li><strong>County Road</strong> - Commercial zone</li>
        <li><strong>Mill Street area</strong> - Revitalized mill district</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Investment Requirements</h2>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Category</th><th>Estimated Cost</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Real Estate (lease)</td><td>$3,000-5,000/mo</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Build-out</td><td>$100,000-180,000</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Total <a href="/guides/maine-dispensary-costs/">Investment</a></td><td>$380,000-700,000</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Success Tips</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Leverage Portland proximity for customer access</li>
        <li>Target the young professional demographic</li>
        <li>Build strong local community presence</li>
        <li>Offer unique products not found in Portland</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="further-reading">
      <h2>Further Reading</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Maine Office of Cannabis Policy (OCP)</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/rules" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Maine Cannabis Rules & Statutes</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="disclaimer">
      <p><em>This is for informational purposes only and does not constitute legal or financial advice. Consult with qualified professionals.</em></p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  article { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .article-header { margin-bottom: 2rem; padding-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .subtitle { font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--color-text-light); }
  section { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  section h2, section h3 { margin-top: 1.5rem; }
  section h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1rem 0; }
  th, td { padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  th { background: var(--color-background); }
  ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .disclaimer { background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffc107; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.875rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
  .further-reading { background: rgba(88, 129, 87, 0.05); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 1rem; margin-top: 3rem; }
  .further-reading h2 { margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.25rem; }
</style>
